==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Astrologer
<hw>As*trol"o*ger</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Astrology</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who studies the stars;
an astronomer.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who practices astrology; one who professes to
foretell events by the aspects and situation of the stars.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Astrologian</ent>⟦br⟧
